{"tid":1569344,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"三個月喇，放棄吧啦，香港人剩係中意玩","createTime":"2019-09-14T14:47:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-28T18:15:06.000Z","uid":120658,"like":14,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"038190ea75ff7ec15c33d00e566187130ba23f13","tid":1569344,"uid":120658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:47:53.000Z","msg":"有感而發.......<br />\n<br />\n三個月以來，每次遊行，集會，不合作運動等等，都有手足被捕，佢地犧牲唔只時間，金錢，仲有自己既前途。<br />\n<br />\n中秋大家唱歌，玩鐳射燈，圍住跑圈的確好開心，搵到方法抒發壓力係應該既。不過節日過左，點解仲要繼續係商場唱歌，嘉年華咁，唱多100,1000次都唔會達到任何一個訴求。<br />\n<br />\n相反黑警同港共政府愈黎愈多陰招，狗招，防不勝防，你地儘管繼續晚晚唱歌自High，我都唔知仲可以講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03e859ef48474b5502043927a8549dd2dbd8c6f0","tid":1569344,"uid":217336,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:49:52.000Z","msg":"一日香港人仲有飯食，有地方住，買得起iphone，一年去到一兩次旅行，一日都唔會有大規模既群眾武力抗爭，算罷喇"},{"pid":"aad1483e88760646369b91e1dcafee099c8b6fce","tid":1569344,"uid":71508,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:50:35.000Z","msg":"分化撚<br />\n你老尾<br />\n哈哈哈"},{"pid":"a6b8c88382552c9ad8acfd3606b0c663df533df8","tid":1569344,"uid":232671,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:51:03.000Z","msg":"唔需要苦行<br />\n最緊要兄弟爬山係爬同一座山，並且係繼續爬，唔好放棄"},{"pid":"b8cdebbb3f855d56e41b8849f097b094424fbbb1","tid":1569344,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:52:37.000Z","msg":"認真戰術冇人進化過<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71b5696909b7988da87194befed2323ccfc82078","tid":1569344,"uid":169992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"038190ea75ff7ec15c33d00e566187130ba23f13","tid":1569344,"uid":120658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:47:53.000Z","msg":"有感而發.......<br />\n<br />\n三個月以來，每次遊行，集會，不合作運動等等，都有手足被捕，佢地犧牲唔只時間，金錢，仲有自己既前途。<br />\n<br />\n中秋大家唱歌，玩鐳射燈，圍住跑圈的確好開心，搵到方法抒發壓力係應該既。不過節日過左，點解仲要繼續係商場唱歌，嘉年華咁，唱多100,1000次都唔會達到任何一個訴求。<br />\n<br />\n相反黑警同港共政府愈黎愈多陰招，狗招，防不勝防，你地儘管繼續晚晚唱歌自High，我都唔知仲可以講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:53:22.000Z","msg":"散水撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你第一段已經解釋咗點解唔可以放棄啦！<br />\n<br />\n唱歌又點、玩燈又點，各有各做唔得？<br />\n<br />\n你有嘜好建議先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb369903198743c90b86a7b28ad7e8bb03be440e","tid":1569344,"uid":120658,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"aad1483e88760646369b91e1dcafee099c8b6fce","tid":1569344,"uid":71508,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:50:35.000Z","msg":"分化撚<br />\n你老尾<br />\n哈哈哈"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:53:22.000Z","msg":"隨你點講啦"},{"pid":"32f6398d0ea931b3f1e02748b79b00edbb470fa4","tid":1569344,"uid":193233,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:53:48.000Z","msg":"不能同意更多，香港人習性真係冇得同共產黨鬥，真係搞集體移民好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"171fabe67429d0513ecf4b571f00f263dad667b0","tid":1569344,"uid":120658,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b8cdebbb3f855d56e41b8849f097b094424fbbb1","tid":1569344,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:52:37.000Z","msg":"認真戰術冇人進化過<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:55:55.000Z","msg":"對家已經可以扮前線，黨鐵圍捕，休班捉人，黎緊都唔知仲有咩招。而我地只係再多幾首歌可以唱，真係唔知點樣光復到香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5536bcb606617fe01b68220ffe197589f74617fd","tid":1569344,"uid":45556,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:56:26.000Z","msg":"分化..."},{"pid":"9ae590b95965d34629cf91ac8c2231dde85de59c","tid":1569344,"uid":290973,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:58:24.000Z","msg":"分敗論<br />\n勿推"},{"pid":"c193c90a01c8ddcbd0e589b874edc1e976429eda","tid":1569344,"uid":377